column5: What's up guys?  looking for somebody to go fishing on friday , im home the hole week going nuts, cant wait for the weekend.  New in toronto , need a fishing body )))
LOL.. welcome to the board... I hope you meant fishing buddy.  I have a fishing body... and it ain't pretty...
You have the body of a Ballerina
That was to much lol TJ your just husky dont forget there are 5 stages of fat your number 3 lol
T.J Takes the "S" out of FAST!!!   lol  :lol:  :lol:  :lol:
take it easy on me guys..)))
TJ is NOT fat, he is just big boned
Or as Eric Cartman says, "I'm Festivly Plump"
No worries serg... were just messing with ya.. but I think im getting the owrst of this one.. festively plump... lol..

I was thinking of taking a pic of myself holding the OFC Community Team #6 sign, but then some of you would have thought I look like I am getting ready to spawn from all the winter feeding.   Wasn't sure what category it would fit in...  Dirk...
what TJ mants to say was "It's not a beer gut...It's a procetive covering for my abs"

However, regardless of how generously proportioned TJ is, the growth on his face is a great distraction from the fact that he is nudging you from 2 feet away. (please don't kick me off the board.......)
